%%{init: {'theme': 'forest'}}%%
flowchart TD
  A[Gateway receives child-node telemetry] --> B[Repackage forwarded payload]
  B --> C[Top-level: sensor keys + envelope fields]
  B --> D[metadata.forwarded=true]
  B --> E[metadata.origin_node_id=CHILD_NODE_ID\nor metadata.origin_imei=CHILD_IMEI]
  B --> F[metadata.route.path=array of hop IDs]
  B --> G[metadata.route.hops=HOP_COUNT]
  B --> H[metadata.route.ingress=INGRESS_LABEL]

  C --> I["Publish as gateway identity\nGATEWAY_IMEI/data"]
  D --> I
  E --> I
  F --> I
  G --> I
  H --> I

  I --> J{Server can recover origin?}
  J -->|Yes| K[Ingest as forwarded\nlink to origin identity]
  J -->|No| L[Mark suspicious\nstore diagnostics]
